== 製作 ==
2015年，在《[[金牌特務_(電影)|金牌特務]]》將要上映時，[[馬克·米勒|馬克·米勒]]與[[馬修·范恩|馬修·范恩]]說，如果電影票房表現良好就有希望推出續集，且范恩表示有興趣執導續集<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2WbhX7QLXxA|title=Kingsman Sequel?  Mark Millar Interview|date=2015-02-04|work=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|accessdate=2016-05-21|archive-date=2016-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401094006/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2WbhX7QLXxA|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joblo.com/movie-news/exclusive-matthew-vaughn-shares-details-on-kingsman-2-and-kick-ass-3-318|title=Exclusive: Matthew Vaughn Shares Details On Kingsman 2 and Kick-Ass 3|publisher=Joblo|last=Maidy|first=Alex|date=2015-02-11|accessdate=2016-05-21|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012224530/http://www.joblo.com/movie-news/exclusive-matthew-vaughn-shares-details-on-kingsman-2-and-kick-ass-3-318|dead-url=no}}</ref>。范恩還指出，他希望[[柯林·佛斯|柯林·佛斯]]能回歸續集，雖然後來報導說佛斯不會繼續參演；而[[馬克·史壯|馬克·史壯]]則表示自己有意回歸<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/colin-firth-kingsman-secret-service-sequel/|title=Colin Firth Could Be Back For Kingsman: The Secret Service Sequel|accessdate=2016-05-21|archive-date=2016-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422155222/http://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/colin-firth-kingsman-secret-service-sequel/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7HLeDo807zM |title=2015 Jameson Empire Awards - Mark Strong |accessdate=2016-05-21 |archive-date=2016-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406230320/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7HLeDo807zM |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年4月29日，[[二十世紀福斯|福斯]]宣布，續集正在計劃中，但還不清楚范恩是否繼續執導<ref>{{cite news|last1=Cunningham|first1=Todd|title=‘Kingsman: The Secret Service’ Sequel in Works at Fox (Exclusive)|url=http://www.thewrap.com/kingsman-the-secret-service-sequel-in-works-at-fox-exclusive/|accessdate=2015-04-30|work=thewrap.com|date=2015-04-29|archive-date=2015-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150501160909/http://www.thewrap.com/kingsman-the-secret-service-sequel-in-works-at-fox-exclusive/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年6月11日，范恩向[[Yahoo|Yahoo]]透露，他已開始撰寫劇本並有望繼續擔任導演<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bovingdon|first1=Edward|title=Matthew Vaughn Confirms Plans For Kingsman 2 (Exclusive)|url=https://uk.yahoo.com/movies/matthew-vaughn-confirms-plans-for-kingsman-2-121271683336.html|accessdate=2015-06-12|work=yahoo.com|date=2015-06-11|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619014545/https://uk.yahoo.com/movies/matthew-vaughn-confirms-plans-for-kingsman-2-121271683336.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 2015年9月，米勒重申，續集正在前製中，且范恩正在想辦法讓佛斯的角色合理的回歸。同月，《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》證實，[[泰隆·艾格頓|泰隆·艾格頓]]簽約參演[[獅門影業|獅門影業]]的《[[羅賓漢崛起|羅賓漢崛起]]》，這將於2016年2月開拍；但這和《金牌特務2》的拍攝行程衝突。10月中旬，兩間片商的調度問題已由他們自行解決。在[[獅門影業|獅門影業]]開始計劃進行《羅賓漢崛起》的前製時，艾格頓決定先拍攝《金牌特務2》，電影預計於2016年4月開拍<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|title=Robin Hood Reboot Pushed for 'Kingsman 2' Shoot (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/robin-hood-reboot-pushed-kingsman-831520|accessdate=2015-10-14|work=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2015-10-12|archive-date=2015-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015175335/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/robin-hood-reboot-pushed-kingsman-831520|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年2月17日，據透露，[[茱莉安·摩爾|茱莉安·摩爾]]在會談飾演反派<ref name="MooreCast">{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|title=Julianne Moore Circling Villain Role for 'Kingsman 2' (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/julianne-moore-circling-villain-role-866626?utm_source=twitterfeed&utm_medium=twitter&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+THRComicCon+%28The+Hollywood+Reporter+-+Heat+Vision%29|accessdate=2016-03-12|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2016-02-17|archive-date=2016-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160221092112/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/julianne-moore-circling-villain-role-866626?utm_source=twitterfeed&utm_medium=twitter&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+THRComicCon+%28The+Hollywood+Reporter+-+Heat+Vision%29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年3月10日，[[荷莉·貝瑞|荷莉·貝瑞]]將會在片中飾演[[中情局|中情局]]領導者的角色，且據傳她簽了兩部片約<ref name="BerryCast">{{cite news|last1=Fleming Jr|first1=Mike|title=Halle Berry In Talks To Star In ‘Kingsman 2’|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/halle-berry-kingsman-2-cia-director-matthew-vaughn-fox-1201718266/|accessdate=2016-03-12|work=Deadline|date=2016-03-10|archive-date=2016-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312020536/http://deadline.com/2016/03/halle-berry-kingsman-2-cia-director-matthew-vaughn-fox-1201718266/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月下旬，范恩證實了貝瑞和摩爾的加入以及正式片名。2016年4月8日，[[佩德羅·帕斯卡|佩德羅·帕斯卡]]加入飾演名為傑克的角色<ref name="PascalCast">{{cite news|last1=Jaafar|first1=Ali|title=‘Games Of Thrones’ Pedro Pascal To Board ‘Kingsman: The Golden Circle’|url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/games-of-thrones-pedro-pascal-kingsman-2-narcos-netflix-halle-berry-julianne-moore-matt-damon-great-wall-china-1201725794/|accessdate=2016-04-08|work=Deadline|date=2016-04-08|language=en-US|archive-date=2016-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408163412/http://deadline.com/2016/04/games-of-thrones-pedro-pascal-kingsman-2-narcos-netflix-halle-berry-julianne-moore-matt-damon-great-wall-china-1201725794/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[查尼·塔圖|查尼·塔圖]]則透過自己的[[Twitter|Twitter]]證實將參演電影。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》證實，[[艾爾頓·強|艾爾頓·強]]正在會談飾演一名關鍵性的角色<ref name="TatumCast">{{cite news|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|title=Channing Tatum Joins the Cast of ‘Kingsman’ Sequel|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/channing-tatum-kingsman-sequel-1201751705/|accessdate=2016-04-15|work=Variety|date=2016-04-13|language=en-US|archive-date=2016-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414125857/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/channing-tatum-kingsman-sequel-1201751705/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月，范恩表示：「這撰寫是我做過最難的事」<ref>{{cite news|title=Matthew Vaughn: Kingsman sequel was tough to write|url=https://www.list.co.uk/article/80201-matthew-vaughn-kingsman-sequel-was-tough-to-write/|accessdate=2016-04-25|work=The List|date=2016-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531214141/https://www.list.co.uk/article/80201-matthew-vaughn-kingsman-sequel-was-tough-to-write/|archive-date=2016-05-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[傑夫·布里吉|傑夫·布里吉]]於2016年5月28日加入劇組<ref name="BridgesCast">{{cite news|last1=Lincoln|first1=Ross A.|title=Jeff Bridges Infiltrates ‘Kingsman: The Golden Circle’|url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/kingsman-the-golden-circle-jeff-bridges-matthew-vaughn-1201764214/|accessdate=2016-05-30|work=Deadline|date=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160529213040/http://deadline.com/2016/05/kingsman-the-golden-circle-jeff-bridges-matthew-vaughn-1201764214/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年6月，[[維尼·瓊斯|維尼·瓊斯]]在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上宣布，他也參演了電影<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/VinnieJones65/status/747162124544315392|title=Vinnie Jones on Twitter|publisher=|accessdate=2016-07-01|archive-date=2019-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701072329/https://twitter.com/VinnieJones65/status/747162124544315392|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但在片中並未出現。

