== 續集和外傳 ==
2017年5月，范恩透露，他和古德曼已有了第三部《金牌特務》電影的計劃<ref>{{cite web|last1=Mitchell|first1=Robert|title=Matthew Vaughn Says Third ‘Kingsman’ Film Already Planned|url=http://variety.com/2017/film/news/matthew-vaughn-third-kingsman-film-already-planned-1202410329/|website=Variety|accessdate=2017-05-05|archive-date=2017-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170506023653/http://variety.com/2017/film/news/matthew-vaughn-third-kingsman-film-already-planned-1202410329/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2017年9月的《Total Film》中，范恩透露，他對《金牌特務3》的反派人選為[[巨石強森|巨石強森]]<ref>''Total Film'' - 2017-09</ref>。他還提到這部續集可能是最後一集，因為他認為《金牌特務》系列該是個三部曲<ref>{{cite web|last1=Watson|first1=Lexi|last2=Jeffery|first2=Morgan|title=Exclusive: Kingsman 3 could be the end of the franchise, with Matthew Vaughn planning a trilogy|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/kingsman/news/a837316/kingsman-3-trilogy-matthew-vaughn-golden-circle-colin-firth-taron/|website=DigitalSpy|accessdate=2017-09-27|archive-date=2017-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929064032/http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/kingsman/news/a837316/kingsman-3-trilogy-matthew-vaughn-golden-circle-colin-firth-taron/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

范恩透露，隨著該系列的成功，他有興趣推出仕特曼的外傳電影<ref>{{cite web|title=HOW MANY KINGSMAN MOVIES MATTHEW VAUGHN PLANS TO MAKE|publisher=CINEMABLEND|author=Chichizola, Corey|url=http://www.cinemablend.com/news/1704450/how-many-kingsman-movies-matthew-vaughn-plans-to-make|date=2017-09-19|accessdate=2017-09-29|archive-date=2017-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170922101006/http://www.cinemablend.com/news/1704450/how-many-kingsman-movies-matthew-vaughn-plans-to-make|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年7月，福斯影片釋出預告確定前傳電影《[[金牌特務：金士曼起源|金牌特務：金士曼起源]]》定於2020年9月上映，后受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]影响，推迟到2021年12月22日<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-03-23|title=Pixar's 'Luca' to Skip Theaters and Debut as Disney+ Exclusive|url=https://www.thewrap.com/pixars-luca-to-skip-theaters-and-debut-as-disney-exclusive/|access-date=2021-03-23|website=TheWrap}}</ref>。

